  schema:name "Brassica oleracea cultivation" ;
  schema:description "Growing protocol for cole crops (cabbage, broccoli, kale, Brussels sprouts), adapted from single species through cultivar selection. Cool-season crops, frost-enhanced flavor. Sow 6–8 weeks before transplant timing; transplant at true-leaf stage. 60–120 days to maturity depending on group." ;
